trans-unit.source: Helps define the type of a SharePoint project item.
trans-unit.target: 帮助定义 SharePoint 项目项的类型。

trans-unit.source: Properties can be set only inside of the <xref:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.ISharePointProjectItemTypeProvider.InitializeType%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: 属性可以设置内部的仅<xref:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.ISharePointProjectItemTypeProvider.InitializeType%2A>方法。

trans-unit.source: <xref:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.ISharePointProjectItemTypeDefinition> allows to associate custom data with a type because it inherits from the <xref:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.IAnnotatedObject> interface.
trans-unit.target: <xref:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.ISharePointProjectItemTypeDefinition> 允许将自定义数据与类型关联，因为它继承自<xref:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.IAnnotatedObject>接口。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the name of the project item type shown in designers.
trans-unit.target: 获取或设置设计器中显示的项目项类型的名称。

trans-unit.source: By default it is the ID.
A string representing a project item type name.
trans-unit.target: 表示项目项类型名称的字符串。

trans-unit.source: Occurs when a startup URL is requested for an <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.ISharePointProjectItem" />.
trans-unit.target: 为 <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.ISharePointProjectItem" /> 请求启动 URL 时会发生。

trans-unit.source: Gets the <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.ISharePointProjectItemType" /> being defined by this <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.ISharePointProjectItemTypeDefinition" /> instance.
trans-unit.target: 获取由此 <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.ISharePointProjectItemTypeDefinition" /> 实例定义的 <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.ISharePointProjectItemType" />。

trans-unit.source: An object representing a project item type.
trans-unit.target: 一个表示项目项类型的对象。

trans-unit.source: Gets an instance of the SharePoint project service.
trans-unit.target: 获取 SharePoint 项目服务的实例。

trans-unit.source: An object representing an instance of the SharePoint project service.
trans-unit.target: 表示的 SharePoint 项目服务实例的对象。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the deployment location of the assembly that is supported by this project item.
trans-unit.target: 获取或设置此项目项支持的程序集的部署位置。

trans-unit.source: An object representing an assembly deployment location.
trans-unit.target: 表示程序集的部署位置的对象。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the scope at which the deployment of the <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.ISharePointProjectItem" /> is supported in SharePoint.
trans-unit.target: 获取或设置 SharePoint 中支持 <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.ISharePointProjectItem" /> 部署的范围。

trans-unit.source: An object representing a project item deployment scope.
trans-unit.target: 表示项目项部署范围的对象。

trans-unit.source: Among other things, <xref:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.ISharePointProjectItemTypeDefinition.SupportedDeploymentScopes%2A> is used in selecting a compatible feature for auto-add, and for restricting the feature and package designer user interfaces.
trans-unit.target: 除了别的之外<xref:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.ISharePointProjectItemTypeDefinition.SupportedDeploymentScopes%2A>中选择兼容的功能包括，为和限制功能和包设计器用户接口使用。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the trust levels in SharePoint supported by the <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.ISharePointProjectItem" />.
trans-unit.target: 获取或设置 <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.ISharePointProjectItem" /> 支持的 SharePoint 中的信任级别。
